{
    "title": "Você Só... Mente",
    "artist": "Noel Rosa",
    "composer": "Noel Rosa / Hélio Rosa",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6/C\">Am6/C</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não espero mais você</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pois você não aparece</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Creio que você se esquece</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(5+)\">A7(5+)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Das promessas que me faz</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6/C\">Am6/C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E depois vem dar desculpas</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Inocentes e banais</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É porque você bem sabe</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que em você desculpo</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Muitas coisas mais</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    O que sei somente</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É que você é um ente</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm\">Gm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que mente inconscientemente</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas finalmente</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não sei porquê</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu gosto imensamente</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(5+)\">A7(5+)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">De você</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6/C\">Am6/C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E Invariavelmente, sem ter o menor motivo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Em um tom de voz altivo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Você quando fala mente</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6/C\">Am6/C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mesmo involuntariamente</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Faço cara de contente</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pois sua maior mentira</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(5+)\">A7(5+)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É dizer à gente que você não mente</span>\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas finalmente</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não sei porquê</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Eu gosto imensamente</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(5+)\">A7(5+)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">De você</span>\n",
